Tidy Dog hopes to train your dog to put away
its toys.

00:02:57.629 --> 00:03:02.319
It uses sensors to detect the weight of a
toy when the dog puts it back in the bin - and

00:03:02.319 --> 00:03:04.000
then dispenses a treat.

00:03:04.000 --> 00:03:06.220
Rewarding your pooch for cleaning up.

00:03:06.220 --> 00:03:11.230
Finally, Firefight Films created Bigger Than
Life - Ice Caves - which is the first documented

00:03:11.230 --> 00:03:20.129
drone flight through ice caves.

